<LP>
   MEDIA: John W. Kluge and Stuart Subotnick, who together
hold about a 40% stake in Image Entertainment Inc., said they
retained Salomon Brothers Inc. "to render financial advisory
and investment banking services" related to the investors'
Image holding. A spokeswoman for the investors said she
couldn't elaborate. Mr. Kluge is chairman and majority owner
of Metromedia Co., based in Secaucus, N.J. Mr. Subotnick is
Metromedia executive vice president and minority owner. Image
Entertainment is a Chatsworth, Calif.-based supplier of laser
disks.
